<span id="freeTextContainer6596910392852042277"><strong>Excellent history lesson!!</strong><br/><br/>This book captured my attention from page 1. I enjoyed reading about many of the influential people who made this great nation what it is today. I learned so much more than when I was a student. On the flip side, I was horrified by the murders committed by Holmes and how much of an evil character he was.</span>

